node.text:
The first GoPro camera was released in 2004...costing around $30. Since it was first introduced GoPro has taken off.

This idea all started becasue founder Nick Woodman just wanted to film himself surfing...in 13 years GoPro went from a small start up company to a $2.3B company.

Some of the "smallest" or "craziest" ideas are the BIG ones that take off. No idea is too small...get after it.

Follow us @businessinstantly
